  <title>WebKit2.Settings.allow_modal_dialogs</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
Settings.allow_modal_dialogs: Boolean (Read / Write / Construct)
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Determine whether it's allowed to create and run modal dialogs
from a <link xref="WebKit2.WebView"/> through JavaScript with
&lt;function&gt;window.showModalDialog&lt;/function&gt;. If it's set to
<code>false</code>, the associated <link xref="WebKit2.WebView"/> won't be able to create
new modal dialogs, so not even the <link xref="WebKit2.WebView-create"/>
signal will be emitted.</p>

